description: Try our easy to follow Mini Doughnuts recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Mini Doughnuts Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: While warm, roll doughnuts in extra caster sugar to coat. Make a hole in one side and fill with jam. Serve warm.
